downloadDescription: Download the sample to integrate a softphone with Dynamics 365 using Channel Integration Framework.
detailsSection: Dynamics 365 Channel Integration Framework is a cloud-to-cloud extensible framework to integrate third-party channel providers with Dynamics 365 Unified Interface Apps using a browser-based JavaScript API library.
systemRequirementsSection: For detailed information about the minimum system requirements, see Channel Integration Frameowrk.
installInstructionSection:
1. To start the download, click Download.
  2. Choose the file to download, and click Next.
  3. You'll be prompted to run or save the file. Click Save to save the file to your computer.
    4. For more information, see Channel Integration Framework.
